WEBVTT

00:13:29.720 --> 00:13:32.016
and actually believe them,

00:13:32.040 --> 00:13:34.360
even if what they're saying
is against you?

00:13:35.320 --> 00:13:37.360
And will you be man enough

00:13:37.680 --> 00:13:41.456
to stand up to other men
when you hear "locker room talk,"

00:13:41.480 --> 00:13:43.816
when you hear stories
of sexual harassment?

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:47.256
When you hear your boys talking
about grabbing ass or getting her drunk,

00:13:47.280 --> 00:13:49.336
will you actually stand up
and do something

00:13:49.360 --> 00:13:51.616
so that one day
we don't have to live in a world

00:13:51.640 --> 00:13:53.376
where a woman has to risk everything

00:13:53.400 --> 00:13:55.456
and come forward
to say the words "me too?"

00:13:55.480 --> 00:13:59.440
(Applause)